Author: coffeecreamer06
Text: This is super hypocritical of me, but eat some. Its low cal anyways, she was nice enough to. If I were her, it would totally hurt knowing you didn't eat a super low cal food someone thought of for you. That's crazy. Everyone i know would just get their own unhealthy foods to eat cause theyyy like it.
